<h2 class="bold font-l">Joseph's Grenade Trick</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When you're a Joestar, grenades and gravity will give you as much time to talk as you want. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TalkingIsAFreeAction" class='trope-example-link'>Talking Is a Free Action</a></p>
