<h1 id="overlay-title">Joseph's Grenade Trick</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
When you're a Joestar, grenades and gravity will give you as much time to talk as you want.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="jbyadf">
